    <h2 class="privacy-section-title text-sm/6 text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-4">Introduction</h2>
    <p class="privacy-text text-sm/6 text-gray-700">
        NorthTX Technologies (“Company,” “we,” “our,” or “us”) respects your privacy and is dedicated to protecting the personal information you share with us. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your information while ensuring transparency and compliance with applicable data protection laws.
    </p>

    <h2 class="privacy-section-title text-sm/6 text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-2">Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul class="privacy-list text-sm/6">
        <li class="text-sm/6 text-gray-700"><strong class="font-semibold text-sm/6">Personal Information:</strong> Full name, email address, phone number, billing information, and other identifiable details.</li>
        <li class="text-sm/6 text-gray-700"><strong class="font-semibold text-sm/6">Technical Information:</strong> IP address, browser type, device specifications, and cookies used for site functionality.</li>
        <li class="text-sm/6 text-gray-700"><strong class="font-semibold text-sm/6">Usage Data:</strong> Insights such as pages visited, time spent on the site, and interactions with site elements.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="privacy-section-title text-sm/6 text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-2">How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul class="privacy-list text-sm/6 text-gray-700">
        <li>Delivering and maintaining web development services to meet your project needs.</li>
        <li>Processing payments and managing transactions securely.</li>
        <li>Communicating updates, progress reports, or inquiries.</li>
        <li>Enhancing website security and improving user experience.</li>
        <li>Complying with relevant legal and regulatory obligations.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="privacy-section-title text-sm/6 text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-2">Disclosure of Information</h2>
    <p class="privacy-text text-sm/6 text-gray-700">
        We do not sell or rent your personal information. Your data may only be shared with trusted third-party service providers, legal authorities, or business partners when necessary for service delivery or compliance with legal requirements.
    </p>

    <h2 class="privacy-section-title text-sm/6 text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-2">Security Measures</h2>
    <p class="privacy-text text-sm/6 text-gray-700">
        We implement advanced security protocols to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, or disclosure. While we strive to secure your data, please note that no online transmission or storage method is completely secure.
    </p>

    <h2 class="privacy-section-title text-sm/6 text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-2">Cookies and Tracking Technologies</h2>
    <p class="privacy-text text-sm/6 text-gray-700">
        Our website uses cookies to enhance functionality and deliver personalized experiences. You can manage your cookie preferences through your browser settings.
    </p>

    <h2 class="privacy-section-title text-sm/6 text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-2">Third-Party Links</h2>
