        Our website may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices or content of these external sites. Please review their respective policies before engaging with them.
    </p>

    <h2 class="privacy-section-title text-sm/6 text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-2">Your Rights and Choices</h2>
    <p class="privacy-text text-sm/6 text-gray-700">
        You may exercise your rights to access, update, or delete your personal data. For assistance, please contact us at <%= mail_to "privacy@northtxtechnologies.com", "privacy@northtxtechnologies.com" %>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="privacy-section-title text-sm/6 text-gray-900 font-semibold mt-2">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
